帆攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水炮車早前在粉嶺機動部隊基地進行演練。梁瑞帆攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁瑞帆攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方近日驅散示威者所用的武力正不斷升級，消息稱警方斥資近2千萬元的三輛水炮車，據報已完成演練。《南華早報》今日更報道，指水炮車最快下月（8月）可出動驅散示威者。消息透露，水炮車將會向示威者噴射液體染料，除了為驅散大量的示威者，也為方便警方拘人。<br />\n<br />\n你可能有興趣的文章<br />\n Belmond傳奇列車彷如時光隧道，帶你重返華麗極致的20年代<br />\nBelmond傳奇列車彷如時光隧道，帶你重返華麗極致的20年代<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.homejournal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.homejournal.com&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=951e0559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.homejournal.com</a><br />\n Huawei set to beat Apple with world's top chip despite US ban<br />\nHuawei set to beat Apple with world's top chip despite US ban<br />\nNikkei Asian Review<br />\n 18 Photos That Look Fake But Are Actually Really Real<br />\n18 Photos That Look Fake But Are Actually Really Real<br />\nAmazing and fun pictures : <a href=\"http://funtof.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffuntof.com&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=54b48d79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">funtof.com</a><br />\n <br />\n私隱聲明 使用條款 聯絡我們<br />\nNext Digital<br />\n<br />\n&copy;2019 AD Internet Limited <br />\nAll rights reserved. 版權所有 不得轉載"},{"pid":"82e7762e6db4fd99576f17c2199249ddc3c0dd2e","tid":1381372,"uid":234831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔好 輕視水炮車威力！<br />\n[文宣！] 水炮車嘅危險性！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320768</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6a9cab74c238afe55d888e7fd6159ccb765f975d","tid":1381372,"uid":234831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff9d0ab4623692a61fd4b2840e1abeffb7abe125","tid":1381372,"uid":292111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:24:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190729/59874412?utm_c